\c 2  
\s1 Yesumna Ukenda Y…®t  
\r (Mat 1:18-25)  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd, Roma mopyam king Kaisa ny…® da Augusto, kea b'ingawa y…®t yoramitonj Roma kantri r…®ga komkesa ny…® b'aramkam gabmani peba wa.  
\v 2 S…® re ongg…®tyam naskajog ny…® b'aramka w…®n awonj, Kwireniyot Roma gabmani mopyam yeb…®m Siriya eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd.  
