\v 4 ∆ó Yosep toda yiwatonj Najaret taun ke Galili eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd de Dawid…®mna taun wa ny…® yogenayo da Betleem Yuda eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, mop nok…®p ton re y…®pa Dawid…®mna b'usmureni b'…®ga na.  
\v 5 ∆ó Yosep yikonj Betleem taun wa re Mariya k…®ma na yana k…®ma re ton t…®r…®r yomnonj molkongga awow…®m. Aj…® Mariya re kom k…®ma na momta B'…®ga ukendam.  
\v 6 ∆ó re ton dea de Betleem wa ebnonda, ti ket w…®n wokatawonj B'…®ga ukendam.  
\v 7 S…® ton ket ti naskajog leo B'…®ga p…®ta yomnonj, …® B'…®ga kukum yomn…®konj kob…®rg…®m ke, ng…®rpu yoramitonj b'angga ongenapu wul iyoki bora wa. Mop nok…®p komkesa obai met re y…®ndang…®r na wekenonj, s…® towa maike ket p…®pmet awonj w…®menam.   
