\p
\v 8 ∆ó ongg…®tyam taun bau ke yap nata n…®nda mamoi y…®r …®pka r…®ga wungawungapu p…®pmet…®nd wekenonj. ∆ó y…®pa s…®w…®ny…®nd ton towaina mamoi y…®rgong omn…®ka eyento.  
\v 9 ∆ó ongg…®t s…®w…®ny…®nd Yonggyam…®mna aneru p…®tap…®ta awonj towa w…®p…®nd, …® ket Yonggyam…®mna b'og…®l …®nyomarenat ten anyowainonj. S…® ton ma sobijog moga na auk…®to.  
\v 10 Aj…® anerut ket ten amninonj da, ‚ÄúGoro moga tainam! Mop nok…®p kon ukoijog sam k…®ma God ma b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t e p…®tap…®ta omny…®n wa p…®lwa r…®nte ra dem komkesa r…®ga wa tainy.  
