\v 52 ∆ó Yesu kea Tina b'og…®l multek…®p ke d…®de Tina uski ke …®n…®ka yikonj. ∆ó God…®m p…®lke d…®de r…®ga wa p…®lke singi b'iyena kea ukoi warabag auka yikenonj.   
\c 3  
\s1 Baptiso Yoan P…®tap…®ta Amninonj Engendam Y…®tkak  
\r (Mat 3:1-12; Mak 1:1-8; Yoan 1:19-28)  
\p
\v 1-2 ∆ó God…®mna bage y…®t ikonj Jakariyamna b'…®ga Yoan…®m p…®lwa wul kesa tungg…®nd ongg…®t w…®n nat re piptin…®m (15) kemag rau Tiberiyom yet re Roma mopyam king Kaisamna p…®pmet…®nd y…®bnonj, …® kwa re Pontiyo Pilato Roma gabmani mopyam yeb…®m Yuda eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Erod king p…®pmet…®nd yeb…®m Galili eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Erod…®mna y…®pa mog ke nany Pilip king p…®pmet…®nd yeb…®m Ituraya eriya d…®de Trokoniti eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Lisaniyo king p…®pmet…®nd yeb…®m Abilene eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Ana d…®de Kayapa y…®na mopyam s…® r…®ga p…®pmet…®nd rebna.  
\v 3 ∆ó Yoan ket yikenonj komkesa Yordan k…®l…®m wuswus tungg nata, …® ton p…®tap…®ta omnena yiyenonj re engenda baptiso na neg…®r m…®le ewaikitam gar ke.  
\v 4 ∆ója naemb j…® ton ongg…®tyam y…®tkak r…®r…®rk…®p omnam p…®tap…®ta yomnenonj r…®nsim re bageyam Isayamna peband …®r…®ki wekeny odede da,  
\q1 ‚Äú∆óta ukoi ara b'emoka p…®ta tainy dem wul kesa tungg…®nd da,  
