\c 4  
\s1 Satana Yesund Otonkena Yiyenonj  
\r (Mat 4:1-11; Mak 1:12-13)  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó Yesu Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga ke y…®ndang…®r omni na y…®raronj Yordan k…®l…®m. S…® Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat Tin w…®p yomnonj wul kesa tungg wa.  
\v 2 Ongg…®t wul kesa tungg…®nd Ton otonkena yokatenonj Satanam p…®lke poti (40) bib…®r k…®ma. ∆ó Ton makwa nangga na awinonj ongg…®t bib…®r w…®ng…®r…®nd. S…® re ket Ton ongg…®tyam bib…®r undwasinonj, s…® Ton ket owoupa awonj.  
\v 3 ∆ó ket Satana Tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúRada Man God…®mna B'…®ga et, Man ingaet ongg…®tyam g…®mo engendam y…®pa sana k…®pol…®m.‚Äù  
\v 4 Aj…® Yesu tin m…®ra yomnonj da, ‚ÄúY…®na peband …®ja emb j…® …®r…®ki y…®b…®m da, ‚ÄòR…®gat ma owou nena kae yilo y…®b…®m.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 5 ∆ó ton ket Yesund yiyonj y…®pa pumbpumb p…®pmet wa, …® Tin ket youyainonj gowukoi komkesa kantri gatab sobijog w…®n…®nd.  
\v 6 ∆ó ket Satana Tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúKon Mor motkainy…®n ongg…®tyam komkesa gowukoi danda d…®de komkesa kantrimna b'og…®l …®nyomarena. Mop nok…®p ongg…®tyam komkesa re kor manaemb nogoninonj, s…® kon r…®r…®r en ti ogonam yena ra kon singi omny…®n.  
\v 7 S…® ongg…®t paemb ra Man ken kumsos net…®mket, komkesa gasa ra ket Mor mima taukanj.‚Äù  
\v 8 Aj…® Yesu tin m…®ra yomnonj da, ‚Äú∆ója emb j…® y…®na peband …®r…®ki y…®b…®m da,  
\q1 ‚ÄòMan moina Yonggyam God…®nd kumsos emkeneny…®t,  
\q2 …® Ti nena mana emb w…®ko omn…®kaeneny…®t.‚Äô‚Äù   
\m
\v 9 ∆ó kwa ket Satana Yesund w…®p yiyonj de Yerusalem taun wa, d…®de Tin yonyitonj y…®pa y…®namet papkak kumb…®nd. ∆ó ton ket Yesund yomnonj da, ‚ÄúRada Man God…®mna B'…®ga et, …®ngkek Man Molenggyam b'atiyakite de gou wa!  
\v 10 Mop nok…®p y…®na peband …®ja emb j…® …®r…®ki y…®b…®m da,  
\q1 ‚ÄòGod opima Tina aneru tengainy dem  
\q2 Men b'obog…®l y…®r engendam.‚Äô   
\m
\v 11 ∆ó kwa …®r…®ki y…®b…®m da,  
\q2 ‚Äò∆ó ton ket men towaina y…®m kumb…®nd motowami.  
\q1 S…® ongg…®t paemb man ma …®ta ket moina p…®s taskis…®t mot…®r kumb…®nd.‚Äô‚Äù   
\m
\v 12 Aj…® Yesu tin m…®ra yomnonj da, ‚ÄúY…®na peband kwa …®ja emb j…® yindeny da, ‚ÄòMan goro moina Yonggyam God…®nd otonkena m…®lend oramiten…®m!‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 13 ∆ó re ket Satana ongg…®tyam komkesa otonkena m…®le undwasinonj, ton ket Yesund y…®raronj, ng…®rpu rokate ra kwa y…®pa b'og…®l w…®n okas otonkenam.  
\v 14 ∆ó ket Yesu Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngamna danda k…®ma na …®tendonj Galili eriya wa, s…® Ti gatab y…®d…®r y…®t re kea kupka eriya nata yikenonj.  
\v 15 ∆ó Ton kea r…®ga ouyaena eyeninonj towaina y…®r opmitenapu met nata, …® kea ket komkesa r…®gap Tin daka esourena yiyeno.   
\s1 R…®gap Yesund Y…®sayo Najaret Taun…®nd  
\r (Mat 13:53-58; Mak 6:1-6)  
\p
\v 16 ∆ó ket Yesu …®tendonj Najaret taun wa r…®k…®nd re Ton ukoi awonj. ∆ó re Ju r…®ga waina w…®ram d…®de y…®r opmitena bib…®r awonj, Ton kea ket yikonj Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met wa Tina get ke m…®le r…®r…®r…®nd, d…®de ket b'…®garonj w…®ng…®r wa, …® ket onyitonj y…®na peba ogenkam.  
\v 17 S…® re y…®na peba owama r…®gat Ti yokawonj bageyam Isayamna eoromki peba, Ton ket peba yobgokonj d…®de oraka yiyonj ongg…®tyam p…®pmet r…®k…®nd re odede y…®tkak …®r…®ki yeb…®m da,   
\q1
\v 18 ‚ÄúYonggyam God…®mna W…®ngaw…®nga …®ta kor p…®l…®nd,  
\q2 mop nok…®p Ton kea ken gaya ke neaukonj  
\q1 Tina b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t p…®tap…®ta omnenam gasa kesa r…®ga wa p…®lwa,  
\q2 …® Ton kea ken n…®tm…®kitonj p…®tap…®ta omnenam Tina m…®le,  
\q1 opi re da …®job…®ki r…®ga …®tr…®ngkam …® y…®rd…®d…® r…®ga y…®r …®pangkam,  
\q2 …® d…®de beb…®g aw…®r omnam towa p…®lke yepim re beb…®g w…®rand wekeny,   
\q1
\v 19 …® kwa p…®tap…®ta omnenam ongg…®tyam kemag r…®denasim ra Yonggyam r…®ga kear tamneniny.‚Äù   
\m
\v 20 ∆ó Ton ket peba yeoromkonj, …® peba owama r…®gam yokawonj. ∆ó re ket Ton omitonj y…®tkak p…®tap…®ta omnenam, komkesa r…®ga yepiya re wekenonj ongg…®t Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met…®nd, adea de Ti p…®lwa y…®r …®sokto.  
\v 21 ∆ó ket Yesu b'atomonj opurena, …® ten amninonj da, ‚ÄúYu kemb …®temb Isayamna …®r…®ki y…®tkak r…®r…®rk…®p ainy ongg…®t opureni y…®tkak ke r…®na re w…®n utkundenya waina y…®pya ke.‚Äù  
\v 22 S…® komkesa r…®gap sam k…®ma y…®t y…®mjateno Ti gatab, …® ton ket k…®d kesa aena wuwenonj Tina tug…®m ke opureni wurar k…®ma y…®tkak gatab, …® ton b'…®gekento da, ‚ÄúR…®ngma, ma …®nte j…® Yosep…®mna B'…®ga?‚Äù  
\v 23 S…® Yesu ten ramnin da, ‚ÄúW…®n opima Korn…®m ongg…®tyam tendam gatab y…®t tendenindam da, ‚ÄòDokta! Man naska molenggyam moina kopa ke b'…®sakende!‚Äô W…®n kwa tendenindam da, ‚ÄòS…®n kea utkundentondam komkesa m…®le r…®na re man amn…®kinot Kaparnaum taun…®nd. S…® ongg…®t paemb man b'ogla kwa d…®k…®nd moinajog tungg…®nd tamn…®kiny…®t ongg…®tyam komkesa m…®le.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 24 ∆ó kwa Ton ten amninonj da, ‚ÄúKon …®m…®njog wen tamniny…®n da r…®gap makwa …®ta bageyam simesime yomn…®kenenyi tinajog tungg…®nd.  
\v 25 ∆ó Kon kwa …®m…®njog wen tamniny…®n da Eliyam w…®n…®nd re piro kesa w…®n awonj nowa kemag d…®de siks (6) mobi k…®ma d…®de ukoi sou aukonj komkesa Israel gow…®nd, ma y…®pa k…®ma mik kongga na wekenonj Israel w…®ng…®r…®nd.  
\v 26 Aj…® ongg…®t w…®n…®nd God maka Eliyand y…®tm…®kitonj towa p…®lwa, aj…® atata b'enga kantri wa, y…®pa mik konggam p…®lwa de Sarepta tungg wa Sidon eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd.  
\v 27 ∆ó kwa ma y…®pa k…®ma leprosi kopa r…®ga na wekenonj Israel w…®ng…®r…®nd ongg…®t w…®n…®nd re Elisa bageyam yeb…®m. Aj…® makwa y…®pa r…®ga k…®lk…®p kesa awonj towa w…®ng…®r…®nd, aj…® …®na y…®paina Siriya r…®ga Naaman nenat.‚Äù  
\v 28 ∆ó re komkesa r…®gap ongg…®tyam y…®tkak gatab utkundento ongg…®tyam Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met…®nd, s…® ton ma sobijog na soro auk…®to.  
\v 29 S…® ton ket ow…®nk…®to, …® ket Yesund otoukena yiyo de taun bau wa, ng…®rpu ket Tin yiyo de ekliti dor y…®u wa r…®k…®nd re ongg…®tyam taun orangi y…®bnonj, nok…®m da Tin …®ski de paga wa.  
\v 30 Aj…® Yesu yikonj re r…®ga bobo …®ny…®ny nat, d…®de ket Ti menon yokatonj.   
\s1 Neg…®r W…®ngaw…®nga ma Okati R…®ga  
\r (Mak 1:21-28)  
\p
\v 31 ∆ó re Yesu yikonj de Kaparnaum taun wa Galili eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, ademb de Ton ket r…®ga ouyaena eyeneninonj ita Ju r…®ga waina w…®ram d…®de y…®r opmitena bib…®r w…®ng…®r…®nd.  
\v 32 S…® r…®ga re k…®d kesa na aena wuwenonj Tina ouyaena gatab, mop nok…®p Tina opureni y…®tkak re danda k…®ma na wuwenonj.  
\v 33 ∆ó ongg…®t Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met…®nd omanda y…®pa Satanamna neg…®r k…®lk…®l w…®ngaw…®nga ma okati r…®ga y…®bnonj, …® ton ket ukoi ara k…®ma obailitonj.  
\v 34 ‚ÄúYaaa! Yaaa! Yesu Najaret tunggam! Nanggamog e Man sowa p…®l…®nd singi yomny…®t? R…®ngma Man neg…®r omna mim s…®n notupiny…®t? Kon wum…®r en yetet Man. Man re God…®mna y…®nay…®na B'…®gatet.‚Äù  
\v 35 Aj…® Yesu …®temb j…® neg…®r w…®ngaw…®nga samany yiyowonj da, ‚ÄúMuma kesa ae! Or opende ti p…®lke!‚Äù ∆ó ket ongg…®t neg…®r w…®ngaw…®ngat ongg…®t r…®gand gou wa sap yotendonj r…®ga wa w…®ng…®r…®nd, ng…®rpu ton ket opendonj ti p…®lke, aj…® ton makwa y…®pa ti k…®pear neg…®r yomnawonj.  
\v 36 Seg ket komkesa r…®ga re k…®d kesa na aena wuwenonj, …® d…®de ket towalenggyam towalenggyam b'arkena wuwenonj da, ‚ÄúNangga y…®tkak e j…®? Ton j…®jab k…®ma d…®de danda k…®ma e neg…®r k…®lk…®l w…®ngaw…®nga yingau, …® ton ket openj.‚Äù  
\v 37 ∆ó ket Yesum gatab y…®d…®r y…®t re kea warabag auka yikenonj komkesa wuswus tungg nata.   
\s1 Yesu Jogjog R…®ga Kopa ke Esakenjinonj  
\r (Mat 8:14-17; Mak 1:29-34)  
\p
\v 38 ∆ó Yesu ket Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met y…®raronj, d…®de ket yikonj Simon…®mna met wa. ∆ó Simon…®mna konggayam jeam re omanda ukoi juwar k…®ma w…®bnonj. S…® r…®gap ket Yesund wum…®r yomno ti gatab.  
\v 39 S…® Yesu ti wus…®nd onyitonj d…®de ket samany y…®t k…®ma juwar weaukenawonj, s…® ket juwar…®t tin w…®raronj. ∆ó ton ket odenja utnyitonj, …® ton ket Yesu d…®de Ton k…®ma meni r…®ga y…®m akainonj.  
\v 40 ∆ó re lom ipanj…®ka yikonj, r…®gap eyento komkesa b'engabenga w…®p kopa k…®ma r…®ga Yesum p…®lwa. S…® Ton y…®pay…®pa kopa r…®ga wa p…®l…®nd y…®m aramiteninonj, …® ket kea ten esakenjinonj.  
\v 41 ∆ó kea kwa neg…®r w…®ngaw…®nga todaka opekto jogjog r…®ga wa p…®lke odede ukoi ara k…®ma da, ‚ÄúMan re God…®mna B'…®ga et.‚Äù Aj…® Ton ten samany eyowinonj d…®de ten eswanginonj y…®t opurenam, nok…®p ton wum…®r na da Ton re Kerisote.   
\s1 Yesu N…®nda Tungg nata Yikenonj God ma Y…®t P…®tap…®ta Omnenam  
\r (Mak 1:35-39)  
\p
\v 42 ∆ó re ket y…®sparonj, Yesu taun ke opendonj d…®de yikonj tintawar wa. ∆ó re r…®ga bobop Tin oraka yiyeno, ton kea Tin yodaro, ng…®rpu ton ket Yesund yogoko da, ‚ÄúGoro s…®n n…®trarin…®m!‚Äù  
\v 43 Aj…® Yesu m…®ra amninonj da, ‚ÄúKon b'ogla God ma pumb tungg gatab God ma b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t p…®tap…®ta omnena iyeny…®n deta kwa n…®nda taun nata, mop nok…®p God ongg…®t r…®l mapenaemb Ken n…®tm…®kitonj.‚Äù  
\v 44 S…® Ton ket kea God ma b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t p…®tap…®ta omnena yiyenonj Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met nata komkesa Yuda eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd.   
\c 5  
\s1 Yesumna Naskajog B'auyaena R…®ga  
\r (Mat 4:18-22; Mak 1:16-20)  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó y…®pa w…®n…®nd re r…®ga bobo God…®mna y…®tkak utkundeno Yesum p…®lke, ton p…®pmet b'…®satena k…®ma Yesund y…®wat…®nto. S…® Ton re onyiti na y…®bnonj Genesaret s…®pa yurund.  
\v 2 ∆ó Ton n…®mog g…®ga y…®r angonj r…®na re s…®pa yurund g…®l wa …®sonati ebnonda. Aj…® kabum …®w…®ka r…®gap kea ongg…®t g…®ga ke g…®l …®pk…®to d…®de ket ton g…®r …®seka nat wekenonj.  
\v 3 ∆ó Yesu y…®pa g…®ga kumb wa angitonj, …®t re Simon…®mna g…®ga. S…® Ton ket Simon…®nd yerkitonj g…®l ke g…®ga …®sonatam sobijog ngai de ny…® wa. ∆ó re r…®gap g…®ga y…®sonato ny…® wa, Yesu ket omitonj g…®ga kumb…®nd, …® …®ngkenaemb ket Ton r…®ga bobo auyaeninonj.  
\v 4 Re ket Ton ouyaena seg awonj, Simon…®nd yomnonj da, ‚ÄúG…®ga yiya kun…®nkun…®n kubol wa, …® amaemb de w…®n ket kabum …®w…®kam g…®r tekoukindam!‚Äù  
