\s1 Marta ake Mariya  
\p
\v 38 ∆ó re ton wuwenonj, nyaw…®nd Yesu b'…®garonj y…®pa tungg w…®ng…®r wa. ∆ó ademb de y…®pa kongga ny…® da Marta Yesund obai omnam y…®ngaukonj.  
\v 39 ∆ó ongg…®t konggam y…®pa kea wundoi w…®bnawonj wogenayo da Mariya. S…® ti wundoi re Yonggyam…®mna p…®s w…®p nat omiti w…®bnonj Tina y…®tkak utkundenam.  
\v 40 Aj…® Marta re nony beb…®g k…®ma na guglam yondratenonj b'engabenga w…®p owou ongonjenam. S…® ton Yesum p…®lwa wikonj d…®de ket Tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúYonggyam-w…®i! Man ma wum…®r et da kor wundoi kor nena mana w…®ko n…®rarkainy? S…® be ngai wingae tin ken y…®m okawam!‚Äù  
\v 41 Aj…® Yonggyam m…®ra tin womnonj da, ‚ÄúMarta, Marta! Man nangga ma gar beb…®g d…®de nony neg…®r ainy…®t jogjog owou ongonjenam?  
\v 42 Aj…® y…®paina m…®le nena e b'og…®ljog omn…®kam d…®k…®nd. Mop nok…®p Mariya re kea b'og…®l p…®pmet yokas, s…® makwa yete ongg…®t p…®pmet ke tin tewaikis.‚Äù   
\c 11  
\s1 Y…®r Opmita gatab Ouyaena  
\r (Mat 6:9-15; 7:7-11)  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó y…®pa w…®n…®nd Yesu y…®pa p…®pmet yokatonj, …® ket y…®r opmitenonj. ∆ó re Ton y…®r opmita seg awonj, Tina b'auyaena r…®ga w…®ng…®r…®nd y…®pa r…®gat Tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúYonggyam! S…®da nouyaenine r…®dede e y…®r opmitena odede r…®ja na re Yoan tina b'auyaena r…®ga auyaeninonj!‚Äù  
\v 2 S…® Yesu ten y…®t etainonj da, ‚ÄúRa w…®n y…®r topmisindam, odede tendenindam da,  
\q1 ‚ÄòAbu! Moina ny…® b'ogla y…®nam rain.  
\q2 ∆ó Moina w…®p omnenapu pumb tungg b'ogla rin…®k ongg…®t gowukoi wa.   
\q1
\v 3 ∆ó bib…®r weanjweanj sowa owou notgoneneniny…®t  
